radiographic_examinations.findings: The uterus is anteverted and measures 9.8 x 4.8 x 5.1 cm. The pigtail catheter in the left adnexa is partially visualized with multiple foci of air. There is small amount of fluid and inflammatory changes seen in the left adnexa extending to the sigmoid colon. No additional undrained fluid collections are visualized, although small residual fluid and air remains in the pocket with catheter in place. The collection appears to extend to the margin of the left ovary. The uterus appears unremarkable.
